    <j.0:title xml:lang="en">PROPOSAL FOR A COUNCIL DECISION GRANTING A COMMUNITY GUARANTEE TO THE EUROPEAN INVESTMENT BANK AGAINST LOSSES UNDER LOANS FOR PROJECTS OF MUTUAL INTEREST IN LATIN AMERICAN AND ASIAN COUNTRIES WITH WHICH THE COMMUNITY HAS CONCLUDED COOPERATION AGREEMENTS (ARGENTINA, BOLIVIA, BRAZIL, CHILE, COLOMBIA, COSTA RICA, ECUADOR, GUATEMALA, HONDURAS, MEXICO, NICARAGUA, PANAMA, PARAGUAY, PERU, SALVADOR, URUGUAY AND VENEZUELA; BANGLADESH, BRUNEI, CHINA, INDIA, INDONESIA, MACAO, MALAYSIA, PAKISTAN, PHILIPPINES, SINGAPORE, SRI LANKA, THAILAND AND VIETNAM)</j.0:title>
    <j.0:dossier_contains_event_legal rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/108025.141464"/>
    <j.0:date_adopted rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1996-12-12</j.0:date_adopted>
